ndees, shows just how much that relationship has deteriorated, and suggests=
 that even this bucolic billionaire enclave is not beyond the reach of Amer=
ica=E2=80=99s current political turbulence.<br/><br/>=F0=9F=8E=99=EF=B8=8F =
<i>Plus: </i>I joined my Puck partner <b>Lauren Sherman</b> on her inimitab=
le <i><u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1l=
