=E2=80=99s sartorial evolution, from <b>Stacey Bendet</b> maximalism to the=
 <b>Zaz</b> bandit aesthetic to <b>Alex Karp</b>=E2=80=99s cyclist chic. Of=
 course, the real power move with this crowd is always quiet luxury and, mo=
re often, quiet practicality. As I noted on the pod, most of these folks di=
dn=E2=80=99t get this rich by stressing their wardrobe.<br/><br/><i>But fir=
